{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was motioned to the right direction, to the left, and went into the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was our goodbye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] As we arrived in the camp, the sign, 'Arbeit macht frei,' even-- you know, I saw that and they explained it, what it means.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That you work, we'll free you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Which we know what it meant-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They shaved us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- we had to undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were ushered into a shower, to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we got these Dutch clogs for our feet, and a cotton uniform, blue and gray striped, with a number on the uniform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was our name from then on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were ordered into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I don't recall-- so many people are talking about which barrack you were in, C, D, and I don't remember. 15-Year-old I was, and by now, I just don't-- can't even recall which barrack I was.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I know I was between two encampments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was two rows of barracks, and then a barbed wire, and then two rows of barracks, and the next encampment.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was in a camp where a lot of Hungarians-- but a lot of gypsies-- were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and the next in camp entered were the Russian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "On the other side was the twins encampment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It's the-- where they collect-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Mengele selected all the twins, out, and they did horrible experiments on them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I saw them dwindling away, day by day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was just they were losing weight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or just one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other was helping the other twins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- they were all ages, from small children to adults.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were all twins in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
